WEBVTT

00:00:27.318 --> 00:00:30.697
I thank all of those who have died...

00:00:38.329 --> 00:00:41.875
I can see the world clearly
again today.

00:00:43.084 --> 00:00:48.298
Say goodbye
to this abominable world.

00:00:49.966 --> 00:00:52.927
There is no turning back.

00:01:07.484 --> 00:01:12.989
Oh, my darling, I don't even know
where my heart has gone

00:01:13.281 --> 00:01:18.912
And I've forgotten
that dream I once had

00:01:19.079 --> 00:01:24.125
Becoming an adult =
keeping a public face and bluffing?

00:01:24.834 --> 00:01:31.049
Tell me, what is reflected
in the painted-over mirror?

00:01:31.674 --> 00:01:36.846
Your photo is starting to fade

00:01:37.388 --> 00:01:41.976
Leaving me, as I change

00:01:41.976 --> 00:01:47.816
I'll shout at the top of my voice
as it pierces through the night

00:01:48.149 --> 00:01:53.613
Burning my chest,
formless fear and all

00:01:53.947 --> 00:01:59.577
It's okay if I can't laugh
like that day

00:01:59.702 --> 00:02:05.416
Sadness, scars, everything...
I want to take them all with me

00:02:06.376 --> 00:02:08.837
You can't kill my vibe, oh baby

00:02:08.837 --> 00:02:11.798
Burning out now,
like a shooting star

00:02:12.173 --> 00:02:14.759
You can't kill my vibe, oh baby

00:02:14.884 --> 00:02:17.512
Burning out now,
like a shooting star

00:02:20.390 --> 00:02:23.893
BLEACH: THOUSAND-YEAR BLOOD WAR

00:02:51.254 --> 00:02:53.798
The stage you created,

00:02:53.798 --> 00:02:56.759
the puddle of blood...
all gone without a trace.

00:03:03.266 --> 00:03:05.935
My innards must have been damaged
somewhere along the way...

00:03:06.352 --> 00:03:10.023
And I can barely hear
because of the explosion...

00:03:10.273 --> 00:03:11.691
This sucks.

00:03:16.112 --> 00:03:17.488
Yachiru!

00:03:17.739 --> 00:03:18.907
Where are you, Yachiru?!

00:03:19.324 --> 00:03:21.951
It's over! Answer me!

00:03:27.749 --> 00:03:29.334
Captain!

00:03:29.459 --> 00:03:31.669
You won, Captain!

00:03:32.170 --> 00:03:36.424
Hey, have you guys
seen Yachiru anywhere?

00:03:36.758 --> 00:03:37.508
Huh?

00:03:37.508 --> 00:03:39.677
No... we haven't.

00:03:39.677 --> 00:03:42.972
Did Lieutenant Kusajishi wander off
somewhere again?

00:03:42.972 --> 00:03:43.890
Find her.

00:03:43.890 --> 00:03:44.933
Huh?

00:03:44.933 --> 00:03:47.185
But we can't sense
her Spiritual Pressure.

00:03:47.393 --> 00:03:48.102
She's not around here—

00:03:48.102 --> 00:03:49.604
Just find her!

00:03:49.812 --> 00:03:51.439
Y-Yes, sir!

00:03:51.606 --> 00:03:52.607
Let's go!

00:03:52.607 --> 00:03:54.442
Spread out and find her!

00:03:56.444 --> 00:03:57.403
Yachiru...

00:04:04.244 --> 00:04:05.078
Captain!

00:04:05.328 --> 00:04:06.120
An ambush?!

00:04:06.537 --> 00:04:07.664
That was dirty!

00:04:07.664 --> 00:04:08.998
You damn brat!

00:04:09.249 --> 00:04:11.459
We're going up against
Kenpachi Zaraki.

00:04:11.876 --> 00:04:13.378
I say it's within reason.

00:04:13.962 --> 00:04:15.922
Get lost or we'll crush you!

00:04:16.256 --> 00:04:17.632
Stop yelling...

00:04:17.924 --> 00:04:19.842
You'll be rid of me soon enough.

00:04:23.596 --> 00:04:24.931
See? Told ya.

00:04:25.390 --> 00:04:27.267
STERN RITTER "G" – LILTOTTO LAMPERD

00:04:29.018 --> 00:04:30.728
You can't go that way.

00:04:33.940 --> 00:04:36.192
Mr. Captain is set to die.

00:04:36.526 --> 00:04:38.736
So it's pointless to rush to his aid.

00:04:38.861 --> 00:04:40.989
STERN RITTER "P" – MENINAS MCALLON

00:04:41.531 --> 00:04:42.699
Whoa!

00:04:42.699 --> 00:04:44.450
W-Wait a minute.

00:04:44.575 --> 00:04:47.203
Shouldn't you guys be going after
your captain instead of me?

00:04:47.370 --> 00:04:48.079
Shut up!

00:04:48.246 --> 00:04:49.914
We know you're trying to kill us
with your weird powers,

00:04:49.914 --> 00:04:51.749
just like the rest!

00:04:51.916 --> 00:04:53.209
You've got it all wrong!

00:04:53.751 --> 00:04:56.754
I don't have that
kind of fighting ability.

00:04:56.879 --> 00:04:59.882
Nothing good will come
from slaying me.

00:05:05.638 --> 00:05:07.015
Uh-oh...

00:05:07.265 --> 00:05:10.018
You all got splashed with my blood.

00:05:10.476 --> 00:05:12.603
Once you're covered in my blood,

00:05:12.729 --> 00:05:17.275
you become a corpse that
only does what I say.

00:05:17.483 --> 00:05:19.277
STERN RITTER "Z" – GISELLE GEWELLE

00:05:19.902 --> 00:05:20.778
Okay!

00:05:20.778 --> 00:05:22.905
Everybody, kill yourselves.

00:05:27.243 --> 00:05:28.786
Protect the Captain!

00:05:28.953 --> 00:05:30.246
Hold your ground!

00:05:30.246 --> 00:05:31.622
Lucky me!

00:05:37.962 --> 00:05:42.467
Those idiots gathered together
so I could kill them all at once!

00:05:42.759 --> 00:05:44.844
STERN RITTER "T" – CANDICE CATNIPP

00:05:49.223 --> 00:05:51.184
Now that all the small fry is gone,

00:05:51.684 --> 00:05:54.896
let's go ahead and take
the Special Threat's head.

00:06:08.826 --> 00:06:10.828
He's not moving like
a guy who's close to dying!

00:06:11.162 --> 00:06:13.956
That's what makes him a Special Threat.

00:06:19.253 --> 00:06:20.880
That was close!

00:06:21.089 --> 00:06:24.217
How is he able to move like that
after fighting Gremmy?

00:06:24.550 --> 00:06:25.802
The guy's a monster!

00:06:31.474 --> 00:06:32.683
You bastards...

00:06:33.059 --> 00:06:34.811
He can still get up?

00:06:35.311 --> 00:06:36.771
Hurry up and die already!

00:06:48.699 --> 00:06:52.745
Nice! You can tell
he's barely alive.

00:06:53.246 --> 00:06:55.164
So, who's gonna finish him off?

00:06:55.540 --> 00:06:57.917
I think we should decide fairly
by rock-paper.

00:06:57.917 --> 00:06:59.877
– I can't move my body...
– And just how do you win that game?

00:06:59.877 --> 00:07:00.670
– I can't move my body...
– Rock wins.

00:07:00.795 --> 00:07:01.963
Then all of us will do rock!

00:07:01.963 --> 00:07:02.880
– Damn it...
– Are you stupid?!

00:07:03.256 --> 00:07:04.966
Is this it for me...?

00:07:06.592 --> 00:07:08.261
Captain Zaraki's
Spiritual Pressure is...

00:07:08.928 --> 00:07:09.929
Calm down, Rukia.

00:07:10.972 --> 00:07:15.101
You still haven't fully recovered
from your previous battle.

00:07:15.435 --> 00:07:16.477
But Brother...!

00:07:24.652 --> 00:07:26.863
Did you feel that, Brother...?

00:07:41.502 --> 00:07:42.879
This Spiritual Pressure...!

00:07:51.345 --> 00:07:52.221
What the...?

00:07:52.889 --> 00:07:54.265
What is that?!

00:07:57.768 --> 00:07:58.728
Uh...

00:07:59.312 --> 00:08:00.938
Is it me, or did that thing just crash...?

00:08:01.731 --> 00:08:02.565
Yeah, it did.

00:08:02.857 --> 00:08:04.066
No way...

00:08:04.484 --> 00:08:05.568
Oww...

00:08:05.943 --> 00:08:07.904
I came in a little too fast...

00:08:10.323 --> 00:08:11.324
When did he—?!

00:08:13.326 --> 00:08:14.410
Hey, what gives?

00:08:14.827 --> 00:08:16.287
You're all beaten up, Kenpachi.

00:08:18.331 --> 00:08:21.959
What are you... doing here?

00:08:23.920 --> 00:08:27.131
I never thought the day would come
when I'd say this to you...

00:08:34.263 --> 00:08:35.473
I came to help you.

00:08:38.935 --> 00:08:42.438
Didn't think there'd ever come
a day when you'd be...

00:08:42.605 --> 00:08:43.940
the one helping me.

00:08:44.649 --> 00:08:45.733
Can you get up?

00:08:46.484 --> 00:08:47.818
Can I get up?

00:08:48.778 --> 00:08:49.946
You fool...

00:08:50.780 --> 00:08:53.741
Worry more about yourself
instead of me.

00:09:21.978 --> 00:09:22.979
What's up with this guy?

00:09:23.813 --> 00:09:25.815
I let my guard down...

00:09:26.440 --> 00:09:28.776
No, you didn't.
This was to be expected.

00:09:28.943 --> 00:09:29.777
Oww...

00:09:29.777 --> 00:09:32.446
That's our Number One
Special Threat...

00:09:32.947 --> 00:09:34.323
Ichigo Kurosaki.

00:09:35.741 --> 00:09:37.868
Shut up!

00:09:38.828 --> 00:09:41.706
"Special Threat"?
"Ichigo Kurosaki"?!

00:09:41.831 --> 00:09:43.541
I don't give a damn!

00:09:44.125 --> 00:09:48.212
Except for the part where
he got me all covered in dust...

00:09:48.963 --> 00:09:50.756
He's gonna pay for that!

00:09:51.716 --> 00:09:53.884
Do you have any idea how early
I have to wake up every day

00:09:53.884 --> 00:09:56.929
before everyone else
so I can do my hair?!

00:09:58.556 --> 00:09:59.890
Ooh... scary...

00:10:00.391 --> 00:10:01.892
That's what she's angry about?

00:10:08.024 --> 00:10:09.692
Galvano Blast!

00:10:13.029 --> 00:10:15.156
Five gigajoules will turn you into ash!

00:10:15.156 --> 00:10:15.781
You piece of shit!

00:10:16.240 --> 00:10:16.907
You idiot.

00:10:17.408 --> 00:10:20.786
One or two shots of
Heilig Pfeil won't kill him.

00:10:33.799 --> 00:10:34.800
See? Told ya.

00:10:45.144 --> 00:10:46.062
So you're here...

00:10:46.520 --> 00:10:48.981
Ichigo Kurosaki.

00:10:55.071 --> 00:10:56.572
Let us begin.

00:10:57.031 --> 00:10:59.909
Haschwalth. Uryu.

00:11:02.161 --> 00:11:03.746
So it's beginning.

00:11:04.580 --> 00:11:05.456
Now...

00:11:06.248 --> 00:11:09.251
will I be among the chosen?

00:11:15.007 --> 00:11:16.884
Damn it!

00:11:20.680 --> 00:11:22.932
You guys did that on purpose,
didn't you?!

00:11:24.433 --> 00:11:25.476
Wow...

00:11:25.476 --> 00:11:26.977
He's strong.

00:11:26.977 --> 00:11:29.939
He parried every single one of
all those shots we fired at him.

00:11:29.939 --> 00:11:31.774
I find him very annoying.

00:11:31.774 --> 00:11:33.192
Wish he was dead.

00:11:33.317 --> 00:11:35.569
We oddly share
the same opinion today.

00:11:35.778 --> 00:11:36.946
I agree with you guys.

00:11:37.113 --> 00:11:39.448
If we all agree,
there's nothing left to discuss!

00:11:41.409 --> 00:11:43.160
I say... we execute him!

00:11:43.619 --> 00:11:44.620
Seriously?

00:11:44.829 --> 00:11:46.831
No way. It makes me tired.

00:11:46.831 --> 00:11:49.500
I don't think it's nice to
slaughter people.

00:11:49.959 --> 00:11:52.128
Fine, then stay there and watch!

00:11:52.628 --> 00:11:56.799
I'll kill the Number One Special Threat
and take all the credit!

00:12:02.346 --> 00:12:03.723
Galvano Javelin!

00:12:07.143 --> 00:12:08.477
Getsugatensho.

00:12:14.442 --> 00:12:15.651
No way...

00:12:22.867 --> 00:12:24.869
Even her Voll Stern Dich couldn't kill him.

00:12:25.202 --> 00:12:26.996
He exceeds our Daten.

00:12:27.246 --> 00:12:28.789
So what should we do?

00:12:29.707 --> 00:12:31.375
Screw it... let's do this.

00:12:32.001 --> 00:12:33.669
Okie-dokie!

00:12:33.878 --> 00:12:35.171
Sklave Rai!

00:12:38.841 --> 00:12:39.842
Sklave Rai.

00:12:43.012 --> 00:12:44.096
Sklave Rai.

00:12:47.975 --> 00:12:49.101
Azhalbiora!

00:12:52.813 --> 00:12:54.064
Pornipora.

00:12:59.820 --> 00:13:00.905
Gagael.

00:13:04.909 --> 00:13:05.868
Dumbbell Duster.

00:13:08.621 --> 00:13:10.790
Dumbbell Duster: Baton Beat.

00:13:13.793 --> 00:13:14.543
Spork.

00:13:19.965 --> 00:13:20.758
Spife.

00:13:31.560 --> 00:13:34.563
Dancing Dead Boys Club!

00:13:46.450 --> 00:13:47.827
Wow!

00:13:51.539 --> 00:13:52.873
Gotcha!

00:13:54.250 --> 00:13:56.669
Munchy Munchy Babies!

00:13:59.922 --> 00:14:02.675
A Special Threat must taste very good.

00:14:03.008 --> 00:14:04.677
Golden Crunch.

00:14:11.183 --> 00:14:12.893
That was too close...

00:14:14.854 --> 00:14:17.273
Dumbbell Duster: Halteres!

00:14:22.278 --> 00:14:23.112
Out of my way!

00:14:29.827 --> 00:14:31.787
Don't go getting cocky!

00:14:32.663 --> 00:14:33.622
Sklave Rai!

00:14:40.462 --> 00:14:41.714
Balbarriel!

00:14:43.883 --> 00:14:45.801
That damn look on your face...

00:14:50.472 --> 00:14:53.392
You can act that way
if you survive this!

00:14:56.270 --> 00:14:58.939
Electrocution!

00:15:04.153 --> 00:15:06.363
Getsuga Jujisho!

00:15:10.743 --> 00:15:12.661
You ain't hitting me with that!

00:15:12.870 --> 00:15:13.746
Dodge, you idiot!

00:15:32.222 --> 00:15:33.432
Damn it...

00:15:33.849 --> 00:15:35.100
Damn it...

00:15:35.976 --> 00:15:37.853
Damn it!

00:15:38.646 --> 00:15:39.647
Gigi, heal me!

00:15:39.772 --> 00:15:41.065
Really?! You sure?

00:15:41.190 --> 00:15:43.567
You idiot! Heal me without
using your blood!

00:15:43.943 --> 00:15:44.818
Boo...

00:15:47.821 --> 00:15:48.405
Here.

00:15:50.741 --> 00:15:52.910
Okay, nicely done.

00:15:53.077 --> 00:15:54.870
Calm down, you bitch.

00:15:55.079 --> 00:15:58.123
Impatience isn't gonna
win you this fight.

00:15:58.540 --> 00:15:59.291
Shut up!

00:16:00.000 --> 00:16:01.919
Here I come, Ichigo Kurosaki!

00:16:02.586 --> 00:16:04.838
I'm gonna kill ya!

00:16:11.053 --> 00:16:11.887
What...?!

00:16:12.680 --> 00:16:15.349
Sorry, but I need you all
to stay dead for a while.

00:16:16.058 --> 00:16:18.644
Bazz-B...you bastard...

00:16:19.353 --> 00:16:21.605
Glory is something that's up for grabs...

00:16:21.730 --> 00:16:24.984
and stealing it is a privilege
of those who show up late.

00:16:25.401 --> 00:16:27.277
Isn't that right,

00:16:27.736 --> 00:16:29.238
Ichigo Kurosaki?

00:16:30.072 --> 00:16:31.824
You make a good point.

00:16:32.324 --> 00:16:34.576
I should've come a bit later.

00:16:34.952 --> 00:16:37.121
But since we all arrived
at the same time,

00:16:37.121 --> 00:16:39.039
what do you say
we share the glory equally?

00:16:41.250 --> 00:16:42.835
Don't be ridiculous.

00:16:43.794 --> 00:16:46.505
The one who kills him
takes all the glory.

00:16:57.266 --> 00:16:59.268
What is... that light?

00:17:05.232 --> 00:17:06.316
Yhwach!

00:17:07.818 --> 00:17:09.111
So it's begun.

00:17:10.946 --> 00:17:12.406
Let us be thankful...

00:17:12.948 --> 00:17:17.786
...to the one who has guided us
to the light.

00:17:19.496 --> 00:17:21.290
Thanks to you,

00:17:21.999 --> 00:17:26.754
I can now invade the Royal Palace.

00:17:42.770 --> 00:17:45.105
The concentration of Reishi
within the Seireitei is dropping!

00:17:45.689 --> 00:17:46.815
What is going on?

00:17:47.149 --> 00:17:49.026
There's a hole...
in the Soul Shield Membrane!

00:17:50.569 --> 00:17:51.403
It means the "key"...

00:17:52.863 --> 00:17:54.782
...has opened the "gate."

00:17:55.783 --> 00:17:59.787
The Shihakusho that Ichigo Kurosaki
is wearing is likely an Ouken

00:17:59.787 --> 00:18:03.874
woven of the bones and hair
of members of Squad Zero.

00:18:04.750 --> 00:18:07.753
Thanks to its durability and
protective qualities,

00:18:07.753 --> 00:18:12.216
Ichigo Kurosaki was able to break
through the seventy-two-layer barrier

00:18:12.216 --> 00:18:16.553
that exists between the Royal Palace
and the Seireitei unscathed.

00:18:17.513 --> 00:18:18.472
However...

00:18:18.680 --> 00:18:22.309
based on the regenerative rate of
the Soul Shield Membrane,

00:18:22.309 --> 00:18:26.772
it will take 6,000 seconds before
the opening can close once more.

00:18:29.233 --> 00:18:31.068
During that interval,

00:18:31.193 --> 00:18:35.489
a rift that allows passage to and from
the Royal Palace has opened.

00:18:37.699 --> 00:18:41.245
POST INVASION – FORMER SQUAD 1 BARRACKS

00:18:38.951 --> 00:18:40.744
I suspected as much, but...

00:18:41.829 --> 00:18:45.541
it appears the Soul King is
the enemy's target, after all...

00:18:46.458 --> 00:18:51.505
THE CENTRAL UNDERGROUND GREAT PRISON – MUKEN

00:18:55.384 --> 00:18:56.176
Damn it!

00:18:57.719 --> 00:18:59.513
Those blasted Squad Zero...

00:18:59.847 --> 00:19:01.849
SQUAD ZERO RIDEN – HYOSUBE'S RIDEN

00:19:02.182 --> 00:19:04.560
What exactly are they thinking...?

00:19:12.109 --> 00:19:15.988
It's pretty naïve to think that
you can go after His Majesty

00:19:15.988 --> 00:19:18.115
when we have you surrounded.

00:19:18.490 --> 00:19:19.908
Diamond Push.

00:19:28.709 --> 00:19:30.586
You're a tough one.

00:19:36.383 --> 00:19:37.718
Burner Finger One!

00:19:38.260 --> 00:19:39.261
Damn it!

00:19:47.811 --> 00:19:48.520
Renji!

00:19:49.271 --> 00:19:50.314
Get going.

00:19:50.731 --> 00:19:52.107
I won't let these guys through.

00:19:52.816 --> 00:19:54.776
I don't know all the details,

00:19:54.902 --> 00:19:57.696
but you have a score to settle
with the boss of the Quincies, right?

00:19:59.615 --> 00:20:00.908
You can have him.

00:20:01.909 --> 00:20:03.577
It's your job now.

00:20:07.164 --> 00:20:08.582
You're not getting away!

00:20:13.921 --> 00:20:15.714
Don't make me repeat myself.

00:20:15.881 --> 00:20:17.716
It makes me look bad.

00:20:22.137 --> 00:20:24.181
I just said you guys are not
getting through!

00:20:29.186 --> 00:20:30.938
Yhwach!

00:20:32.189 --> 00:20:33.315
Allow me...

00:20:50.415 --> 00:20:51.625
Ishida...!

00:20:52.209 --> 00:20:53.919
What're you doing there?!

00:20:54.753 --> 00:20:56.421
Leave, Kurosaki.

00:20:56.630 --> 00:20:57.214
What?

00:20:58.006 --> 00:21:00.676
You cannot stop His Majesty.

00:21:02.010 --> 00:21:04.680
What're you talking about, Ishida...?

00:21:05.597 --> 00:21:09.101
Leave... before you waste your life.

00:21:09.518 --> 00:21:13.021
I'm asking you
what're you doing there?!

00:21:24.283 --> 00:21:25.575
Licht Regen.

00:21:44.761 --> 00:21:45.762
Ishida...

00:21:46.346 --> 00:21:47.264
Ishida...

00:21:53.103 --> 00:21:53.895
Wait!

00:21:53.895 --> 00:21:56.606
You still haven't answered
any of my questions!

00:21:57.399 --> 00:21:59.443
Have you finished your farewells?

00:21:59.776 --> 00:22:00.569
Yes.

00:22:02.112 --> 00:22:04.781
It will be an eternal parting.

00:22:06.950 --> 00:22:08.160
I am fully aware of that.

00:22:17.085 --> 00:22:18.086
Ishida!

00:22:19.880 --> 00:22:21.298
Say something...

00:22:29.222 --> 00:22:31.099
Ishida!

00:22:43.945 --> 00:22:48.241
All at once, the lights went out

00:22:48.241 --> 00:22:49.534
Reminding me

00:22:49.534 --> 00:22:50.827
with a voice

00:22:50.827 --> 00:22:52.788
and I cannot move

00:22:53.705 --> 00:22:57.959
Unable to convey even a millimeter

00:22:57.959 --> 00:23:00.504
of the lines that I dubbed

00:23:00.504 --> 00:23:02.798
All lines
that I don't want to forget

00:23:02.798 --> 00:23:04.174
Rewound

00:23:04.174 --> 00:23:05.300
Repeated

00:23:05.300 --> 00:23:06.385
Became a mark

00:23:06.385 --> 00:23:07.761
And I notice the dust

00:23:07.761 --> 00:23:08.804
I wait and wait

00:23:08.804 --> 00:23:10.305
But it won't start

00:23:10.305 --> 00:23:11.473
If it's already ended

00:23:11.473 --> 00:23:12.682
I give up

00:23:12.682 --> 00:23:13.934
But can I

00:23:13.934 --> 00:23:15.143
borrow your shoulder?

00:23:15.268 --> 00:23:16.812
With that knife

00:23:16.812 --> 00:23:18.814
that was left behind

00:23:19.856 --> 00:23:21.858
Pierce it through

00:23:21.858 --> 00:23:23.151
Still

00:23:23.151 --> 00:23:25.487
in the middle of a dream,

00:23:25.487 --> 00:23:27.989
We kept searching

00:23:27.989 --> 00:23:30.158
For the scar that

00:23:30.158 --> 00:23:32.869
the revolving world remembers

00:23:32.869 --> 00:23:35.122
With just the strong desire

00:23:35.122 --> 00:23:38.500
to keep on living

00:23:38.500 --> 00:23:43.672
We'll choose a tomorrow
that will not return

00:23:43.672 --> 00:23:48.385
In just a little while

00:23:48.385 --> 00:23:52.681
The final curtain will fall

00:23:53.598 --> 00:23:57.102
Shining upon us

00:23:57.102 --> 00:24:00.021
The blurred end roll

